  "translations": {
    "en": "O! Hisham indeed Allah Most High he says in His Book indeed in that ldhkra for whoever kan for him qlb means 'ql and said and lqd We gave lqman wisdom said alfhm and the intellect O! Hisham indeed Luqman said labnh twad' llhq be not most rational the people and indeed alkys lda the truth easy O! bny indeed the worldly life bhr 'myq indeed/already ghrq in it (f) 'alm kthyr fltkn sfyntk in it (f) tqwa of Allah and hshwha faith and shra'ha reliance and qymha the intellect and dlylha knowledge and skanha patience",
    "ur": "اے Hisham بے شک Allah Most High he says میں His Book بے شک میں that ldhkra for whoever kan for him qlb means 'ql اور said اور lqd We gave lqman wisdom said alfhm اور the intellect اے Hisham بے شک Luqman said labnh twad' llhq be not most rational the people اور بے شک alkys lda the truth easy اے bny بے شک the worldly life bhr 'myq indeed/already ghrq in it (f) 'alm kthyr fltkn sfyntk in it (f) tqwa of Allah اور hshwha faith اور shra'ha reliance اور qymha the intellect اور dlylha knowledge اور skanha patience",
    "tr": "ey Hisham muhakkak Allah Most High he says içinde His Book muhakkak içinde that ldhkra for whoever kan for him qlb means 'ql ve said ve lqd We gave lqman wisdom said alfhm ve the intellect ey Hisham muhakkak Luqman said labnh twad' llhq be not most rational the people ve muhakkak alkys lda the truth easy ey bny muhakkak the worldly life bhr 'myq indeed/already ghrq in it (f) 'alm kthyr fltkn sfyntk in it (f) tqwa of Allah ve hshwha faith ve shra'ha reliance ve qymha the intellect ve dlylha knowledge ve skanha patience",
    "fa": "ای Hisham به درستی Allah Most High he says در His Book به درستی در that ldhkra for whoever kan for him qlb means 'ql و said و lqd We gave lqman wisdom said alfhm و the intellect ای Hisham به درستی Luqman said labnh twad' llhq be not most rational the people و به درستی alkys lda the truth easy ای bny به درستی the worldly life bhr 'myq indeed/already ghrq in it (f) 'alm kthyr fltkn sfyntk in it (f) tqwa of Allah و hshwha faith و shra'ha reliance و qymha the intellect و dlylha knowledge و skanha patience",
    "id": "wahai Hisham sesungguhnya Allah Most High he says di dalam His Book sesungguhnya di dalam that ldhkra for whoever kan for him qlb means 'ql dan said dan lqd We gave lqman wisdom said alfhm dan the intellect wahai Hisham sesungguhnya Luqman said labnh twad' llhq be not most rational the people dan sesungguhnya alkys lda the truth easy wahai bny sesungguhnya the worldly life bhr 'myq indeed/already ghrq in it (f) 'alm kthyr fltkn sfyntk in it (f) tqwa of Allah dan hshwha faith dan shra'ha reliance dan qymha the intellect dan dlylha knowledge dan skanha patience",
    "bn": "হে Hisham নিশ্চয়ই Allah Most High he says মধ্যে His Book নিশ্চয়ই মধ্যে that ldhkra for whoever kan for him qlb means 'ql এবং said এবং lqd We gave lqman wisdom said alfhm এবং the intellect হে Hisham নিশ্চয়ই Luqman said labnh twad' llhq be not most rational the people এবং নিশ্চয়ই alkys lda the truth easy হে bny নিশ্চয়ই the worldly life bhr 'myq indeed/already ghrq in it (f) 'alm kthyr fltkn sfyntk in it (f) tqwa of Allah এবং hshwha faith এবং shra'ha reliance এবং qymha the intellect এবং dlylha knowledge এবং skanha patience",
    "es": "oh Hisham ciertamente Allah Most High he says en His Book ciertamente en that ldhkra for whoever kan for him qlb means 'ql y said y lqd We gave lqman wisdom said alfhm y the intellect oh Hisham ciertamente Luqman said labnh twad' llhq be not most rational the people y ciertamente alkys lda the truth easy oh bny ciertamente the worldly life bhr 'myq indeed/already ghrq in it (f) 'alm kthyr fltkn sfyntk in it (f) tqwa of Allah y hshwha faith y shra'ha reliance y qymha the intellect y dlylha knowledge y skanha patience",
    "fr": "ô Hisham certes Allah Most High he says dans His Book certes dans that ldhkra for whoever kan for him qlb means 'ql et said et lqd We gave lqman wisdom said alfhm et the intellect ô Hisham certes Luqman said labnh twad' llhq be not most rational the people et certes alkys lda the truth easy ô bny certes the worldly life bhr 'myq indeed/already ghrq in it (f) 'alm kthyr fltkn sfyntk in it (f) tqwa of Allah et hshwha faith et shra'ha reliance et qymha the intellect et dlylha knowledge et skanha patience",
    "de": "o Hisham wahrlich Allah Most High he says in His Book wahrlich in that ldhkra for whoever kan for him qlb means 'ql und said und lqd We gave lqman wisdom said alfhm und the intellect o Hisham wahrlich Luqman said labnh twad' llhq be not most rational the people und wahrlich alkys lda the truth easy o bny wahrlich the worldly life bhr 'myq indeed/already ghrq in it (f) 'alm kthyr fltkn sfyntk in it (f) tqwa of Allah und hshwha faith und shra'ha reliance und qymha the intellect und dlylha knowledge und skanha patience",
    "ru": "о Hisham поистине Allah Most High he says в His Book поистине в that ldhkra for whoever kan for him qlb means 'ql и said и lqd We gave lqman wisdom said alfhm и the intellect о Hisham поистине Luqman said labnh twad' llhq be not most rational the people и поистине alkys lda the truth easy о bny поистине the worldly life bhr 'myq indeed/already ghrq in it (f) 'alm kthyr fltkn sfyntk in it (f) tqwa of Allah и hshwha faith и shra'ha reliance и qymha the intellect и dlylha knowledge и skanha patience",
    "zh": "啊 Hisham 确实 Allah Most High he says 在 His Book 确实 在 that ldhkra for whoever kan for him qlb means 'ql 和 said 和 lqd We gave lqman wisdom said alfhm 和 the intellect 啊 Hisham 确实 Luqman said labnh twad' llhq be not most rational the people 和 确实 alkys lda the truth easy 啊 bny 确实 the worldly life bhr 'myq indeed/already ghrq in it (f) 'alm kthyr fltkn sfyntk in it (f) tqwa of Allah 和 hshwha faith 和 shra'ha reliance 和 qymha the intellect 和 dlylha knowledge 和 skanha patience"
